--- compilation on windows
wxDev-C++ (http://wxdsgn.sourceforge.net/) project file is included.
You could also use the Makefile.win with mingw if you change lines 
11-13 according to your system.
binary will be in bin/win

--- compilation on linux
you'll need libwxgtk2.8-dev libgtk2.0-dev and its dependencies,
also scons must be installed, then just run
"scons" from a terminal in whatever directory you extracted the
archive into.
binary will be in bin/linux